function transferFrom(address from, address to, uint256 tokenId)

function updateFighter(uint256 _tokenId, tuple(uint256 tokenId, string name, uint256 level, uint256 wins, uint256 hp, uint256 strength, uint256 dexterity, uint256 agility, uint256 intelligence, uint256 durability, uint256 location, string fighterType) _fighter)
